<div class="title">An Accident and a Failed Sobriety Test</div>
<div class="substance">Zolpidem (Ambien), Alprazolam (Xanax) & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Scarious&Exact=1">Scarious</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Scarious. "An Accident and a Failed Sobriety Test: An Experience with Zolpidem (Ambien), Alprazolam (Xanax) & Alcohol (exp50123)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 22, 2010. erowid.org/exp/50123</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
